original: FORNANDER, Johan Martin Natanael, Direktör, Sundsvall, f Växjö 9/11 84 av spar-bksdir A F o Karin Fahlström, gm Ruth Browall. Studex, offex, KHS, utb v AB Sthlmssyst. Off Kronob reg 09—27, kapt övgst 27—36, i res sed. 36. Kontr.förest Svls utskänkn.AB 27—30, disp 31—38, vkst dir Svls systemAB sed. 38. Kyrkoflm. Huv.m Svls sparbk, ordf Svls kyrkobrödrakår, H.-sands stifts kyrkobr konv.råd, Svls soldat-heni, sekr o kass Svls ungdomsgård, kass Svls underst- o studiefond, led styr f Svls församl.hus, Sv kyrkans lekm.frb, kyrkobr gen.råd, styrordf Smal gille i Svl, KFUMs scoutkårs kårkvarter. RSO. Hobbies: Sång, musik, litteratur (spec religiös, livsåskådn.-filos o psykol).
translated: FORNANDER, Johan Martin Natanael, Director, Sundsvall, b. Växjö 9/11/84 to the Bank Director A F and Karin Fahlström, m. Ruth Browall. Graduate, Civil servant, High School of Sundsvall, trained at AB Stockholmssyster. Officer in the Kronoberg Regiment 1909-1927, Captain from 1927-1936, resigned from active duty in 1936. Contract Manager at Svls utskänkn.AB 1927-1930, Deputy Manager from 1931-1938, Managerial Director at Svls systemAB since 1938. Church official. Main manager of Svls savings bank, Chairman of Svls church brotherhood, Member of the Church brotherhood council of the Diocese of Härnösand, Secretary and Treasurer of Svls youth center, Treasurer of Svls support and study fund, member of the board of Svls parish house, member of the board of the Swedish Church's lay association, member of the general council of the Church brotherhood, Chairman of the board of Smal gille in Svl, Scoutmaster's quarters of KFUMs scout corps. Order of the Seraphim. Hobbies: Singing, music, literature (especially religious, worldview-philosophy and psychology).
